Subviewer 2.0
=============

  Extension:

    ".sub"

  Tags:

    <b>bold</b>
    <i>italic</i>
    <u>underline</u>

  Notes:

    In the header: COLF is "&H" followed by RRGGBB; STYLE is "st" for
    strikeout, "ud" for underline, "bd" for bold, or "it" for italic; SIZE is
    font size in points; FONT is font name.

  Sources:

    http://forum.doom9.org/showthread.php?p=542288#post542288
